full_text:
AJ Brown was in a category of his own in 2020. His avg. targeted air yards was >10yd and he still had an avg. YAC above expectation of 2.6yds. 

Also look at how similar Jerry Jeudy was in his rookie campaign to DK Metcalf's 2020
#nflverse #NFLTwitter https://t.co/u83F4tzcp3

Did some performance checks today with dplyr, data.table and @collapse_R and I can’t emphasize enough how insanely fast collapse is. I recommend every #nflverse and #rstats user to check that package out. It’s efficient and lightweight.
https://t.co/8nzn2wlvv2
